activity_month.group_desc1_1: Obtain a hero through Advanced Summons in the Hall of Heroes.
activity_month.group_desc1_2: Obtain a hero through Oracle Temple summons.
activity_month.group_desc1_3: Obtain Hero Shards from the Forgotten Land.
activity_month.group_desc2_2: Take part in Arena to obtain gear and gear refinement materials.
activity_month.group_desc2_3: Take part in Yggdrasil Supremacy to obtain gear and gear enchantment materials.
activity_month.group_desc3_1: Obtain a Relic by praying at the Relic Vault.
activity_month.group_desc3_2: Obtain a Relic by performing Prayer Points at the Relic Vault.
activity_month.group_desc3_3: Obtain Relic Shards from the Labyrinth.
activity_month.group_desc4_1: Obtain Terra Crystals by planting flowers in the Gloomwoods.
activity_month.group_desc4_2: Obtain Terra Crystals by pillaging in the Gloomwoods.
activity_month.group_desc4_3: Obtain Terra Crystals by playing Terra Occupation in the Gloomwoods.
activity_month.group_desc5_1: Obtain a Rune from Celestial Trials.
activity_month.note_reward_desc4: When the event starts, the default reward is a Selectable Divine/Demon hero. The reward becomes 6,000 Diamonds after the server is open for 30 days.
activity_month.bubble1: You're almost at today's {0} point goal! You'll have to try a little harder to get the Divine/Demon Selectable Card on the last day! (Check the Guide for tips.)
activity_month.note_reward_day_desc: Claim rewards once per day for the first 30 days of a server opening!
